# Form Conventions (Zod + React Hook Form)

---

## 1. Folder Structure

```
randomz-fe/
└── schemas/
    └── {entity}.ts     # Zod schemas & inferred form types
```

---

## 2. Zod Schemas

Define schemas in `schemas/{entity}.ts`. Derive form types with `z.infer` — never write them by hand.

```ts
// schemas/room.ts
import { z } from "zod"

export const roomRequestSchema = z.object({
  name: z
    .string()
    .min(1, "Tên phòng không được để trống")
    .max(50, "Tên phòng tối đa 50 ký tự"),
  description: z.string().max(200, "Mô tả tối đa 200 ký tự").optional(),
  currentMode: z.enum(["CLASSIC", "SPEED", "TEAM"], {
    required_error: "Vui lòng chọn chế độ chơi",
  }),
  duration: z
    .number({ invalid_type_error: "Thời gian phải là số" })
    .min(1, "Tối thiểu 1 phút")
    .max(120, "Tối đa 120 phút"),
})

export type RoomFormValues = z.infer<typeof roomRequestSchema>
```

> `RoomFormValues` (từ Zod) dùng cho form. `RoomRequest` (từ `types/`) dùng khi gọi API. Hai type thường giống nhau nhưng tách biệt để tránh coupling.

---

## 3. Form với React Hook Form + Zod

### Dạng cơ bản (không dùng shadcn/ui)

```tsx
"use client"

import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"
import { zodResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/zod"
import { useTransition } from "react"
import { roomRequestSchema, type RoomFormValues } from "@/schemas/room"
import { createRoomAction } from "../actions"
import { ApiError } from "@/lib/api"

export function CreateRoomForm() {
  const [isPending, startTransition] = useTransition()

  const {
    register,
    handleSubmit,
    formState: { errors },
    setError,
    reset,
  } = useForm<RoomFormValues>({
    resolver: zodResolver(roomRequestSchema),
    defaultValues: {
      name: "",
      currentMode: "CLASSIC",
      duration: 10,
    },
  })

  function onSubmit(values: RoomFormValues) {
    startTransition(async () => {
      try {
        await createRoomAction(values)
        reset()
      } catch (e) {
        setError("root", {
          message: e instanceof ApiError ? e.message : "Đã có lỗi xảy ra",
        })
      }
    })
  }

  return (
    <form onSubmit={handleSubmit(onSubmit)}>
      <div>
        <input {...register("name")} placeholder="Tên phòng" />
        {errors.name && <p className="text-sm text-destructive">{errors.name.message}</p>}
      </div>

      <div>
        <select {...register("currentMode")}>
          <option value="CLASSIC">Classic</option>
          <option value="SPEED">Speed</option>
          <option value="TEAM">Team</option>
        </select>
        {errors.currentMode && <p className="text-sm text-destructive">{errors.currentMode.message}</p>}
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          {...register("duration", { valueAsNumber: true })}
          type="number"
          placeholder="Thời gian (phút)"
        />
        {errors.duration && <p className="text-sm text-destructive">{errors.duration.message}</p>}
      </div>

      {errors.root && <p className="text-sm text-destructive">{errors.root.message}</p>}

      <button type="submit" disabled={isPending}>
        {isPending ? "Đang tạo..." : "Tạo phòng"}
      </button>
    </form>
  )
}
```

### Dạng shadcn/ui (dùng `<Form>` provider)

```tsx
"use client"

import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"
import { zodResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/zod"
import { useTransition } from "react"
import { Form, FormControl, FormField, FormItem, FormLabel, FormMessage } from "@/components/ui/form"
import { Input } from "@/components/ui/input"
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { roomRequestSchema, type RoomFormValues } from "@/schemas/room"
import { createRoomAction } from "../actions"
import { ApiError } from "@/lib/api"

export function CreateRoomForm() {
  const [isPending, startTransition] = useTransition()

  const form = useForm<RoomFormValues>({
    resolver: zodResolver(roomRequestSchema),
    defaultValues: { name: "", currentMode: "CLASSIC", duration: 10 },
  })

  function onSubmit(values: RoomFormValues) {
    startTransition(async () => {
      try {
        await createRoomAction(values)
        form.reset()
      } catch (e) {
        form.setError("root", {
          message: e instanceof ApiError ? e.message : "Đã có lỗi xảy ra",
        })
      }
    })
  }

  return (
    <Form {...form}>
      <form onSubmit={form.handleSubmit(onSubmit)} className="space-y-4">
        <FormField
          control={form.control}
          name="name"
          render={({ field }) => (
            <FormItem>
              <FormLabel>Tên phòng</FormLabel>
              <FormControl>
                <Input placeholder="Nhập tên phòng" {...field} />
              </FormControl>
              <FormMessage />
            </FormItem>
          )}
        />

        {/* other fields */}

        {form.formState.errors.root && (
          <p className="text-sm text-destructive">{form.formState.errors.root.message}</p>
        )}

        <Button type="submit" disabled={isPending}>
          {isPending ? "Đang xử lý..." : "Tạo phòng"}
        </Button>
      </form>
    </Form>
  )
}
```

---

## 4. Loading States

### `useTransition` — dùng khi gọi Server Action trong handler

```tsx
const [isPending, startTransition] = useTransition()

function handleDelete() {
  startTransition(async () => {
    await deleteRoomAction(id)
  })
}

<button disabled={isPending} onClick={handleDelete}>
  {isPending ? "Đang xoá..." : "Xoá"}
</button>
```

### `useFormStatus` — dùng cho submit button bên trong `<form action={...}>`

```tsx
import { useFormStatus } from "react-dom"

function SubmitButton({ label }: { label: string }) {
  const { pending } = useFormStatus()
  return (
    <button type="submit" disabled={pending}>
      {pending ? "Đang xử lý..." : label}
    </button>
  )
}
```

> `useFormStatus` chỉ hoạt động khi button nằm **bên trong** `<form>` có `action={serverAction}`.

---

## 5. Required Packages

```bash
npm install zod @hookform/resolvers react-hook-form
```

---

## Rules

- Zod schema là source of truth cho validation — đặt trong `schemas/`.
- Luôn dùng `z.infer<typeof schema>` để derive form type, không viết tay.
- Lỗi từ server map vào `setError("root", ...)` hoặc field cụ thể nếu backend trả về field errors.
- Loading state dùng `useTransition` (handler) hoặc `form.formState.isSubmitting` (submit).
- Dùng `valueAsNumber: true` khi register input `type="number"`.
